name: The pearls
description: The pearls of the giant onychophores are left on their way, nobody knows exactly what they are for, it is not known if they are their offspring ... A mystery surrounds these pearls that are leaving their way, perhaps this war is not the end. .. many ponder the possibility of a new beginning. This music expresses the surprise when finding the first pearls, perhaps there is a way to avoid the definitive extinction.
